snippet.title: Choko loco 2 - trailer. Game by Jinxtengu.
snippet.description:
This is a trailer of the upcoming 3D adult game Choko loco 2 by Jinxtengu, which is scheduled for release on October 28, 2024.
Check it out on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3272830/Choko_loco_2/
Download link for games on Jinxtengu website: http://www.revengeofthesunfish.com/gamesarc.html
The link to the site itself is from Jinxtengu: http://www.revengeofthesunfish.com/
Link to the Jinxtengu channel: https://www.youtube.com/user/Revengeofthesunfish
